    substitutionRule: "When Chesapeake blue crab is unavailable, Dungeness crab picked into lump portions provides a comparable texture and sweetness, though the flavor is milder and benefits from a slight increase in the Worcestershire component. Frozen claw meat may never substitute for backfin or jumbo lump in a finished cake.",
